Ruby">Ruby</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sapphire" title="Sapphire">Sapphire</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sodalite" title="Sodalite">Sodalite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sunstone" title="Sunstone">Sunstone</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tanzanite" title="Tanzanite">Tanzanite</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tiger%27s_Eye" title="Tiger's Eye">Tiger's Eye</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Topaz" title="Topaz">Topaz</a></div>
